          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1663752104405-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1663752104405-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1663752104405-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>peeled garlic</strong> and 3/4 of your <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>(save the rest for later!) to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your <strong>basil</strong>,<strong> soft cheese</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>creamy pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a food processor? Chop the ingredients and grind to a paste in a pestle & mortar instead!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663752112198-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663752112198-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663752112198-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663752112198-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663752112198-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>creamy pesto</strong> and <strong>salmon flakes</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>pasty filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1663752120582-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1663752120582-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1663752120582-x700.jpg",
